    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have started to brown, increase the oven temperature to 240ºC/ 220ºC (fan)/gas 9</p><p>Add the <strong>stock</strong> and return the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> to the oven for 15-20 min further or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has thickened to a gravy-like consistency – this is your <strong>herby roast chicken tray bake</strong></p>",
